  <description>
    <p>The GameOutlet put together the latest deals in games for PC. It puts the deals for the most
      popular online game stores in one single place. It allows you to easily find the best deals
      and search for your favorite games</p>
    <p>Features</p>
    <ul>
      <li>See the latest deals from the most popular game stores</li>
      <li>Search by a game title to see its prices on these stores</li>
      <li>Save your favorite games to a wishlist</li>
      <li>See all deals from the online game stores</li>
      <li>Light and dark theme</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
